The full interactive API docs are available at **http://localhost:8000/docs** (Swagger UI) and **http://localhost:8000/redoc** when the server is running.

### Key Endpoint Groups

| Group | Endpoints | Description |
|-------|-----------|-------------|
| Auth | `POST /auth/token` | Issue JWT token |
| Scans | `POST /scans`, `GET /scans`, `GET /scans/{id}` | Core scan management |
| Scan Actions | `/scans/{id}/xss`, `/sqli`, `/ssti`, `/graphql`, `/smb`, `/snmp`, `/ldap`, `/banners`, `/ssl`, `/dns`, `/linpeas`, `/privesc`, `/narrative`, `/methodology`, `/exploit-chain`, `/osint` | Per-scan feature modules |
| Loot | `POST /loot`, `GET /loot`, `GET /loot/summary` | Loot management |
| Listeners | `POST /listeners`, `GET /listeners`, `POST /listeners/{port}/send` | Shell catchers |
| MSF | `GET /msf/status`, `POST /msf/run`, `GET /msf/sessions` | Metasploit RPC |
| Tools | `POST /tools/file-transfer`, `GET /tools/tty-upgrade`, `POST /tools/jwt/analyze` | Standalone tools |
| OSINT | `POST /osint/domain`, `/osint/ip`, `/osint/email`, `/osint/person` | OSINT engine |
| AI | `POST /ai/chat`, `GET /ai/status` | Ollama AI assistant |
| Plugins | `GET /plugins`, `POST /plugins`, `PATCH /plugins/{name}`, `DELETE /plugins/{name}`, `POST /plugins/{name}/reload` | Plugin management |
| Reporting | `POST /scans/{id}/report`, `/scans/{id}/htb-report`, `/scans/{id}/obsidian` | Report export |

